-- Angola’s Sonangol to Boost Stake in Banco Comercial, Diario Says
-- B y   H e n r i q u e   A l m e i d a
-- 2012-06-14T06:42:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-14/angola-s-sonangol-to-boost-stake-in-banco-comercial-diario-says.html
 Angolan oil company Sonangol EP
plans to take part in  Banco Comercial Portugues SA (BCP) ’s 500-
million-euro capital increase and bolster its stake in the
Portuguese bank, Diario Economico reported, without saying how
it got the information.  Banco Comercial aims to carry out the capital increase in
July or in September at the latest and is preparing a road show
to present the operation to international investors, according
to the Portuguese newspaper.  Click here for web link   To contact the reporter on this story:
